}]]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-red-600","children":"What if the client says they haven't been paid yet?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed","children":["This is a common \"pass-the-buck\" tactic. Your contract is with THEM, not their client. Be firm: \"I understand that, but our project was completed [Date] and our ",["$","$L8",null,{"href":"/blog/best-invoice-software-for-small-business","className":"text-red-600 underline","children":"standard terms"}]," apply.\""]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-red-600","children":"Should I keep working if they owe me?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed","children":"NO. Stop all work immediately. Late payment is a violation of contract. Continuing to work only increases your \"exposure\" and gives them more leverage. Pause the job until the balance is $0."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-red-600","children":"How do I branded my escalation?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed","children":["Maintain the same professional ",["$","$L8",null,{"href":"/blog/how-to-send-an-invoice-by-email-professionally","className":"text-red-600 underline","children":"email tone"}]," even when the situation gets tense. Losing your temper makes you look unprofessional and can even hurt you if the case ever goes to mediation or court."]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-red-600 rounded-[5rem] p-24 text-center shadow-3xl relative overflow-hidden group","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-7xl font-black text-white mb-10 font-outfit uppercase tracking-tighter italic","children":"Get Paid What You're Owed"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-red-50 text-2xl mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-bold","